# Copy to .env.local if you want to override locally (optional).
#
# Production / Dokploy — set this in the frontend service environment so it is
# available at `vite build` time (build args / env in Dokploy UI):
#   VITE_API_URL=https://api.predictionking.lukemiller.dev
# Use the same URL scheme (http vs https) as visitors use in the browser.
#
# Local dev — leave unset; vite.config.ts proxies /api → http://localhost:5166
